Trinity CLARA - DARPA PA-25-07-02 Submission Package
Copyright 2026 Trinity S³AI (t27) Project

This product includes software developed by the Trinity S³AI (t27) Project
for the DARPA CLARA (Common Learning Repository for AI) solicitation
PA-25-07-02.

Project Repository: https://github.com/gHashTag/trinity-clara
Main Repository: https://github.com/gHashTag/t27

The Trinity S³AI (t27) Project is a research initiative focused on
ternary computing architectures for AI reasoning, including:
- Kleene K3 ternary logic for automated reasoning
- Vector Symbolic Architecture (VSA) for compositional reasoning
- Bounded rationality with restraint mechanisms
- Explainable AI with proof trace limitations

This submission package contains formal specifications, examples, and
evidence demonstrating compliance with DARPA CLARA requirements for
Technical Area 1 (Argumentation & Reasoning) and Technical Area 2
(Composition).
